1975;;Naked Came The Stranger;;American;;Radley Metzger;;Alan Marlow, Darby Lloyd Rains, David Savage;;adult film;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Naked_Came_The_Stranger_(1975_film);;Gilly, a radio host, is determined to enjoy herself with friends and acquaintances as much as her playful husband Billy. Gilly enjoys herself in several locations around New York City, including at an elaborate dress ball, an old-fashioned ballroom and on the top floor of a double-decker bus while it drives around the city.[1]